Recruiting support for administrative and professional services projects across the U.S. The Recruiter will be expected to perform the following tasks/activities:
1. Post anonymous job ads; 
2. Review applicant resumes;
3. Review resumes of potential candidates on relevant job boards (e.g., indeed);
4. List all qualified candidates in an MS Excel spreadsheet;
5. Using a company-provided list of questions, screen qualified candidates via phone;
6. Note candidate responses to each question;
7. Rate the strength of each candidates&#039; match for subject position;
8. Provide an organized package of resumes, candidate responses to questions, ratings, and a contact listing for all applicants/candidates regardless of whether they participated in a phone screen. The objective is to screen all qualified applicants/candidates. Unscreened candidates must be identified on the candidate listing.
